Class Customer

java.lang.Object
  Customer

public class Customer
extends Object

Customer class keeps the information of the customer. It saves the address and the account that ties with it. If a new customer is to be serviced, then customer class will have all the method to complete the process. The customer class also gives the id of every customer that later would be used as identification for other class.

Version:
0.2
Author:
